channel.description:
Hello, I have recently been working on a Runescape Private Server Webclient maker. I am 100% going to edit the site more and more every day. Rune-Wiki is a private server community and is evolving each and ever day. Finally after a few weeks I have created a Runescape Private Server Webclient Maker.
This webclient maker features:
[img]http://i40.tinypic.com/2a7sn8.jpg[/img]
Plain Website
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/jrvz5.jpg[/img]
Forums
[IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/3e26pl.jpg[/img]
Premium and Normal Control Panels (This is the normal one)
[img]http://i39.tinypic.com/w8wol.jpg[/img]
(This is the premium one)
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/30twya.jpg[/img]
100% working webclient creation
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/23i6gw.jpg[/img]
Fully Working Control Panel Login
[IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/vipkp.jpg[/img]
Fully Working Premium Control Panel Login
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/v6izf.jpg[/img]
Fully Working Premium Activation Codes
The site is at :D :D
This webclient maker will be offered as a script release within time. My scripts are edited by me, please give some credits to tobex because im almost 99% sure that is where the begining scripts came from. (I did some research and I guess someone hacked him and got some files from tobex) I dont really know the story, but anyway the scripts that I edited were most likely FROM tobex.
I am also going to edit more of them as the time goes on. (for example add more tools that can be used)
As for if I release my scripts it will be on that site. Please come and enjoy the community as it is so far. Thanks
PS: Theme for the site that I used in pictures will be changed latter on and the ones that are in pictures are leached from chocotemplates.
~Mike & iSmile
